OL,3,CIsland electricity bills to be
OL,4,Csubsidised for the rest of the year
OL,6,FAlderney residents and businesses will
OL,7,Fbenefit from a subsidy to offset the
OL,8,Frise in global oil prices.
OL,10,FThe States of Alderney will allocate
OL,11,F#200,000 from the island's limited
OL,12,Freserves to help soften the blow of
OL,13,Fthe short-term price hikes.
OL,15,FIt follows ongoing unrest and
OL,16,Fdisruption in the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,17,Flimiting supply and forcing prices to
OL,18,Fskyrocket.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
