OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784917111
OL,3,CIsland electricity bills to be
OL,4,Csubsidised for the rest of the year
OL,6,FJeannie Cameron, the Chair of
OL,7,FAlderney's Policy and Finance
OL,8,FCommittee, told ITV News: "The cost of
OL,9,Felectricity is 106% more than in
OL,10,FGuernsey, and that's using the
OL,11,Fstandard rate in Guernsey, not the off-
OL,12,Fpeak rate.
OL,14,F"That is because we have to generate
OL,15,Four electricity from fuel, and fuel
OL,16,Fprices here have what's called a 'fuel
OL,17,Fcost component'.
OL,19,F"That makes the cost of it here
OL,20,Fexceedingly expensive."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784917111
OL,3,CIsland electricity bills to be
OL,4,Csubsidised for the rest of the year
OL,6,FNow the island's power provider is
OL,7,Fkeen to reduce the amount of imports
OL,8,Fto protect itself from soaring global
OL,9,Foil prices.
OL,11,FJon Stokes, the Head of Technical
OL,12,FEngineering at Alderney Electricity
OL,13,FLimited, told ITV News in a statement:
OL,14,F"Oil prices have swung wildly with the
OL,15,Fconflict in Iran and the threat to the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz - Brent has been
OL,17,Fclose to $100 a barrel this week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784917111
OL,3,CIsland electricity bills to be
OL,4,Csubsidised for the rest of the year
OL,6,F"We have no cable to France, we are
OL,7,Fnear 100% reliant on hydrocarbons, and
OL,8,Fwe sit at the end of a very long and
OL,9,Fdelicate supply chain.
OL,11,F"That is exactly why AEL is pushing
OL,12,Fahead with renewables - solar projects
OL,13,Falready underway, with battery storage
OL,14,Fand a larger solar farm in planning.
OL,16,F"Renewables mean real energy security,
OL,17,Fless pollution and fewer emissions -
OL,18,Fall of which makes Alderney a better
OL,19,Fplace to live."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
